1. What is a server
-> A server is simply a computer which is accessible by clients only on the network. This kind of server is called client-server-model.
2. What is the role of the domain name 
-> Domain name is used to assign an IP address which is very large for human to remember.
-> So DNS serves this work and make easy by remembering the only assigned readable name.
3. What type of DNS record www is in www.foobar.com
-> www.foobar.com is "A record" type of DNS which point to the main domain name of Ip address.
4. What is the role of the web server 
-> A web server is a software or hardware that accepts http or secure http request and returns http respond as the content of the resource.
5. What is the role of the application server
-> To install, operate and host applications
-> Distributing and monitoring software updates 
-> Processing data sent from another web server
6. What is the role of database
-> The role of the database in this website infrastructure is used to store, manipulate and remove data
7. What is the server using to communicate with the computer of the user requesting the website
-> The communication between computers is occur on the internet through TCP/IP protocol
8 The issue on this infrastructure
-> Amonge many SPOF(Single Point of Failure) that may happen, there may be failerity of database server.
9. Downtime when maintenance needed (like deploying new code web server needs to be restarted)
-> Check all components of the infrastructure, check that may be power case(turned off) of the server
10. Cannot scale if too much incoming traffic
-> It is hard to scale if there is too much incoming traffic becuase one server contains all components of infrastructure 

